  "instructions": [
    "In a blender, blend glutinous rice, amazake, sesame oil, ginger, green chili peppers, and garlic until smooth.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a saucepan and add soy sauce, fermented bean paste, and water. Bring to a boil over high heat.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Meanwhile, cook the ssam wraps according to package instructions.",
    "Spoon the hot amazake mixture into the cooked ssam wraps.",
    "Garnish with scallions and serve immediately."
  ],
